286
00:28:15,829 --> 00:28:17,244
Padre Stewart.

287
00:28:18,142 --> 00:28:19,454
Olá Douglas.

288
00:28:20,662 --> 00:28:21,949
Vejo que está lendo.

289
00:28:21,973 --> 00:28:22,802
- Sim.

